<keyLead box="[151,1436,386,408]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">8. Inner branch of male cerci is distinctly longer than the outer one................................................ 9</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="61.[151,1437,151,672]" box="[151,1436,415,437]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">
<keyLead box="[151,1436,415,437]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">- Branches of male cerci almost similar in length, or the outer branch a little longer than the inner one.................. 10</keyLead>
